cast.overview: Supervillains Harley Quinn, Bloodsport, Peacemaker and a collection of nutty cons at Belle Reve prison join the super-secret, super-shady Task Force X as they are dropped off at the remote, enemy-infused island of Corto Maltese.
cast.title: The Suicide Squad

details.biography: Maya was born on March 28, 2011 in San Diego, CA. Since birth, Maya was a sidekick to her older sister (Olivia) to all of her auditions and bookings. That changed in December of 2014, when Maya asked if she could follow in her footsteps. One of her first auditions was for The Thundermans, and history was made as she landed the role of Chloe Thunderman. Fun Fact: Chloe and Maya share the same birth date.
details.name: Maya Le Clark
